  <div class="text-center w-2/3 mx-auto">
    <h2 class="my-4">A BIT MORE ABOUT US</h2>

    <p class="my-4">One Church Brighton is a broad and inclusive
    church, full of brilliant but imperfect people who are trying
    to work out how the Christian faith makes sense in the real
    world.</p>

    <p class="my-4">Spend much time with us and you'll hear us
    speak of our values. We see these as orientating stories that
    shape our shared practice together and guide the decisions we
    take. So in order to understand what we do, you need to
    understand why we do it. Our values unpack this:</p>

    <div class="mt-4 mb-12">
      <p><span class="highlight">Intimacy</span> with God</p>

      <p><span class="highlight">Involvement</span> in the
      world</p>

      <p><span class="highlight">Interdependence</span> with each
      other</p>

      <p><span class="highlight">Inclusion</span> of everyone</p>

      <p><span class="highlight">Integrity</span> in all we do</p>
    </div>
